For in app messaging:https://dotnet.microsoft.com/en-us/apps/aspnet/signalr Summary of ASP.NET with SignalRASP.NET SignalR is a real-time communication library that enables bi-directional communication between clients and the server. It's perfect for chat applications, live notifications, and real-time updates.How It WorksClient Sends a Request: A user performs an action (e.g., sending a message).SignalR Hub Receives It: The server processes the request in a Hub, which acts as a central point for handling real-time messages.Broadcast to Clients: The hub pushes updates to connected clients without them having to refresh the page.